    {
      "text": "小兔子乖乖，把门开开。妈妈回来了，快点开门！",
      "translation": "Good little rabbit, open the door. Mom is back, open up quickly!"
    },
    {
      "text": "不开不开，我不开。妈妈没回来，谁来都不开。",
      "translation": "Won't open, won't open, I won't open. Mom hasn't come back, no matter who comes I won't open."
    }
  ],
